"SyncdWWANa RfeNaR PodRRRR FreRA"
Prefetch=0:x=F,0:y=W,1:y=F,1:x=T
Com=Rf Fr
Orig=SyncdWWANa RfeNaR PodRRRR FreRA

{

0:rx=x; 0:ry=y;
1:ry=y; 1:rx=x;

}

 P0                | P1           ;
 li r2,1           | ll r2,0( ry) ;
 Loop00:           | ll r3,0( rx) ;
 ll r3,0( rx)      |              ;
 ori r9992,r2,0      |              ;
 sc r9992,0( rx)     |              ;
 beq r9992,0,Loop00 |              ;
 sync              |              ;
 li r4,1           |              ;
 sw r4,0( ry)      |              ;
exists
(x=1 /\ 0:r3=0 /\ 1:r2=1 /\ 1:r3=0)


Observed outcomes:
369: x=1 0:r3=0 1:r2=0 1:r3=0 
293: x=1 0:r3=0 1:r2=0 1:r3=1 
338: x=1 0:r3=0 1:r2=1 1:r3=1 
NOT OBSERVED

"RfeAA SyncdRWANa Rfe PodRR FreNaA"
Prefetch=1:x=F,1:y=W,2:y=F,2:x=T
Com=Rf Rf Fr
Orig=RfeAA SyncdRWANa Rfe PodRR FreNaA

{

0:rx=x;
1:rx=x; 1:ry=y;
2:ry=y; 2:rx=x;

}

 P0                | P1                | P2           ;
 li r2,1           | Loop01:           | lw r2,0( ry) ;
 Loop00:           | ll r2,0( rx)      | lw r3,0( rx) ;
 ll r3,0( rx)      | ori r9992,r2,0      |              ;
 ori r9992,r2,0      | sc r9992,0( rx)     |              ;
 sc r9992,0( rx)     | beq r9992,0,Loop01 |              ;
 beq r9992,0,Loop00 | sync              |              ;
                   | li r3,1           |              ;
                   | sw r3,0( ry)      |              ;
exists
(x=1 /\ 0:r3=0 /\ 1:r2=1 /\ 2:r2=1 /\ 2:r3=0)


Observed outcomes:

"Rfe SyncdRWNaA RfeANa PodRRNaR FreRNa"
Prefetch=1:x=F,1:y=W,2:y=F,2:x=T
Com=Rf Rf Fr
Orig=Rfe SyncdRWNaA RfeANa PodRRNaR FreRNa

{

0:rx=x;
1:rx=x; 1:ry=y;
2:ry=y; 2:rx=x;

}

 P0           | P1                | P2           ;
 li r2,1      | lw r2,0( rx)      | lw r2,0( ry) ;
 sw r2,0( rx) | sync              | ll r3,0( rx) ;
              | li r3,1           |              ;
              | Loop00:           |              ;
              | ll r4,0( ry)      |              ;
              | ori r9992,r3,0      |              ;
              | sc r9992,0( ry)     |              ;
              | beq r9992,0,Loop00 |              ;
exists
(y=1 /\ 1:r2=1 /\ 1:r4=0 /\ 2:r2=1 /\ 2:r3=0)


Observed outcomes:
19: y=1 1:r2=0 1:r4=0 2:r2=1 2:r3=0 
37: y=1 1:r2=1 1:r4=0 2:r2=1 2:r3=1 
346: y=1 1:r2=1 1:r4=0 2:r2=0 2:r3=1 
160: y=1 1:r2=0 1:r4=0 2:r2=0 2:r3=1 
142: y=1 1:r2=0 1:r4=0 2:r2=1 2:r3=1 
95: y=1 1:r2=1 1:r4=0 2:r2=0 2:r3=0 
201: y=1 1:r2=0 1:r4=0 2:r2=0 2:r3=0 
NOT OBSERVED

 li r2,1           | lw r2,0( rx)      | ll r2,0( ry)      ;
 Loop00:           | sync              | Loop02:           ;
 ll r3,0( rx)      | li r3,1           | ll r3,0( rx)      ;
 ori r9992,r2,0      | Loop01:           | ori r9992,r3,0      ;
 sc r9992,0( rx)     | ll r4,0( ry)      | sc r9992,0( rx)     ;
 beq r9992,0,Loop00 | ori r9992,r3,0      | beq r9992,0,Loop02 ;
                   | sc r9992,0( ry)     |                   ;
                   | beq r9992,0,Loop01 |                   ;
exists

2:ry=y; 2:rx=x;

 Loop00:           | sync              | Loop02:           ;
 ll r3,0( rx)      | li r3,1           | ll r3,0( ry)      ;
 ori r9992,r2,0      | Loop01:           | ori r9992,r2,0      ;
 sc r9992,0( rx)     | ll r4,0( ry)      | sc r9992,0( ry)     ;
 beq r9992,0,Loop00 | ori r9992,r3,0      | beq r9992,0,Loop02 ;
                   | sc r9992,0( ry)     | li r4,1           ;
                   | beq r9992,0,Loop01 | sw r4,0( rx)      ;
exists
(x=2 /\ y=2 /\ 0:r3=1 /\ 1:r2=2 /\ 1:r4=0 /\ 2:r3=1)

==========W+RWC==========

"RfeAR PodRWRA WseAA PodWRAA FreAA"
Prefetch=1:x=F,1:y=W,2:y=F,2:x=T
Com=Rf Ws Fr
Orig=RfeAR PodRWRA WseAA PodWRAA FreAA

{

0:rx=x;
1:rx=x; 1:ry=y;
2:ry=y; 2:rx=x;

}

 P0                | P1                | P2                ;
 li r2,1           | ll r2,0( rx)      | li r2,2           ;
 Loop00:           | li r3,1           | Loop02:           ;
 ll r3,0( rx)      | Loop01:           | ll r3,0( ry)      ;
 ori r9992,r2,0      | ll r4,0( ry)      | ori r9992,r2,0      ;
 sc r9992,0( rx)     | ori r9992,r3,0      | sc r9992,0( ry)     ;
 beq r9992,0,Loop00 | sc r9992,0( ry)     | beq r9992,0,Loop02 ;
                   | beq r9992,0,Loop01 | Loop03:           ;
                   |                   | ll r4,0( rx)      ;
                   |                   | ori r9992,r4,0      ;
                   |                   | sc r9992,0( rx)     ;
                   |                   | beq r9992,0,Loop03 ;
exists
(x=1 /\ y=2 /\ 0:r3=0 /\ 1:r2=1 /\ 1:r4=0 /\ 2:r3=1 /\ 2:r4=0)

Prefetch=1:x=F,1:y=W,2:y=F,2:x=T
Com=Rf Ws Fr
Orig=RfeNaA SyncdRWAA WseANa PodWRNaA FreANa

{

0:rx=x;
1:rx=x; 1:ry=y;
2:ry=y; 2:rx=x;

}

 P0           | P1                | P2                ;
 li r2,1      | Loop00:           | li r2,2           ;
 sw r2,0( rx) | ll r2,0( rx)      | sw r2,0( ry)      ;
              | ori r9992,r2,0      | Loop02:           ;
              | sc r9992,0( rx)     | ll r3,0( rx)      ;
              | beq r9992,0,Loop00 | ori r9992,r3,0      ;
              | sync              | sc r9992,0( rx)     ;
              | li r3,1           | beq r9992,0,Loop02 ;
              | Loop01:           |                   ;
              | ll r4,0( ry)      |                   ;
              | ori r9992,r3,0      |                   ;
              | sc r9992,0( ry)     |                   ;
              | beq r9992,0,Loop01 |                   ;
exists
(x=1 /\ y=2 /\ 1:r2=1 /\ 1:r4=0 /\ 2:r3=0)

==========WWC+po+porp==========
MIPS A
"Rfe PodRW RfeNaR PodRWRNa Wse"
Prefetch=1:x=F,1:y=W,2:y=F,2:x=W
Com=Rf Rf Ws
Orig=Rfe PodRW RfeNaR PodRWRNa Wse

{

0:rx=x;
1:rx=x; 1:ry=y;
2:ry=y; 2:rx=x;

}

 P0           | P1           | P2           ;
 li r2,2      | lw r2,0( rx) | ll r2,0( ry) ;
 sw r2,0( rx) | li r3,1      | li r3,1      ;
              | sw r3,0( ry) | sw r3,0( rx) ;
exists
(x=2 /\ 1:r2=2 /\ 2:r2=1)


Observed outcomes:
48: x=2 1:r2=0 2:r2=1 
71: x=2 1:r2=2 2:r2=0 
235: x=1 1:r2=0 2:r2=1 
93: x=2 1:r2=1 2:r2=0 
100: x=2 1:r2=0 2:r2=0 
87: x=1 1:r2=2 2:r2=1 
141: x=1 1:r2=2 2:r2=0 
104: x=1 1:r2=1 2:r2=0 
121: x=1 1:r2=0 2:r2=0 
NOT OBSERVED

==========WWC+pora+poaa+A==========
MIPS A
"RfeAR PodRWRA RfeAA PodRWAA WseAA"
Prefetch=1:x=F,1:y=W,2:y=F,2:x=W
Com=Rf Rf Ws
Orig=RfeAR PodRWRA RfeAA PodRWAA WseAA

{

0:rx=x;
1:rx=x; 1:ry=y;
2:ry=y; 2:rx=x;

}

 P0                | P1                | P2                ;
 li r2,2           | ll r2,0( rx)      | Loop02:           ;
 Loop00:           | li r3,1           | ll r2,0( ry)      ;
 ll r3,0( rx)      | Loop01:           | ori r9992,r2,0      ;
 ori r9992,r2,0      | ll r4,0( ry)      | sc r9992,0( ry)     ;
 sc r9992,0( rx)     | ori r9992,r3,0      | beq r9992,0,Loop02 ;
 beq r9992,0,Loop00 | sc r9992,0( ry)     | li r3,1           ;
                   | beq r9992,0,Loop01 | Loop03:           ;
                   |                   | ll r4,0( rx)      ;
                   |                   | ori r9992,r3,0      ;
                   |                   | sc r9992,0( rx)     ;
                   |                   | beq r9992,0,Loop03 ;
exists
(x=2 /\ y=1 /\ 0:r3=1 /\ 1:r2=2 /\ 1:r4=0 /\ 2:r2=1 /\ 2:r4=0)


Observed outcomes:
332: x=1 y=1 0:r3=0 1:r2=2 1:r4=0 2:r2=0 2:r4=2 
14: x=1 y=1 0:r3=0 1:r2=1 1:r4=0 2:r2=0 2:r4=2

Prefetch=1:x=F,1:y=W,2:y=F,2:x=W
Com=Rf Rf Ws
Orig=RfeNaR PodRWRA RfeAR PodRWRA WseANa

{

0:rx=x;
1:rx=x; 1:ry=y;
2:ry=y; 2:rx=x;

}

 P0           | P1                | P2                ;
 li r2,2      | ll r2,0( rx)      | ll r2,0( ry)      ;
 sw r2,0( rx) | li r3,1           | li r3,1           ;
              | Loop00:           | Loop01:           ;
              | ll r4,0( ry)      | ll r4,0( rx)      ;
              | ori r9992,r3,0      | ori r9992,r3,0      ;
              | sc r9992,0( ry)     | sc r9992,0( rx)     ;
              | beq r9992,0,Loop00 | beq r9992,0,Loop01 ;
exists
(x=2 /\ y=1 /\ 1:r2=2 /\ 1:r4=0 /\ 2:r2=1 /\ 2:r4=0)
